<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="rocky mountain ecology">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Rocky Mountain ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
In the alpine zone with dwarf willows, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Dryas" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Dryas" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Dryas</taxonomicName>
